column5: Thanks for the update Steve...Thought I might see some brave (?) souls out there closer to your marina mouth.   Cheers  Craig
as long as you were not stroking it with the music LOL!!!!  all alone just you your camera and ice!!!!

Glad to see you back out on the ice today... Didn't look like that would happen till atleast Tuesday...  Mother nature, or is it Jack Frost certainly has a sense of humour this year...  BRRRR it got cold fast  Cheers,  Jen
